cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with improving machine translation using sequence models and neural networks. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses feed-forward neural networks to train the models. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with improving the performance of machine translation systems. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also possible as the paper uses neural networks to train the models. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with modeling reordering operations in machine translation, which can be seen as a pattern recognition problem.
